            <p>Operations are active along the <a href="https://example.com/route-sylhet-dhaka" target="_blank">Sylhet-Dhaka Road</a>, which has reopened after severe flooding.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rescue-routes">
            <h3>Route 3: Khulna to Jessore</h3>
            <p>The <a href="https://example.com/route-khulna-jessore" target="_blank">Khulna-Jessore Route</a> is a major rescue path after the cyclone disaster in Khulna.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

